::Shredder::

Shredder nods, his eyes a bit wide. Info was running through his head, making 
quick assumptions and the like. Unicron? Destrons? Quientessions? The 
Tripredacus Council? Shredder was a bit confused, but managed to sort most of 
the information.

"So if Unicron revived the Judge and now you are him, you were just with 
Unicron?" he asks, jumping to a conclusion.
